(1, 'Cho Ro Sui 朝露翠', 'ceremonial', 5, 0, 'First Flush (May)', '100% Hand Picked, 100% First Flush, 40 Days Shaded, Stone Milled Matcha. Morning dew freshness, vibrant green. Premium Ceremonial Grade - $59/30g retail.', 1, NOW(), NOW()),
(1, 'Saemidori Competition Grade さえみどり', 'ceremonial', 5, 0, 'First Flush (May)', 'Competition grade matcha using Saemidori cultivar, handpicked. Exceptionally smooth, sweet umami. Competition Grade - $75/30g retail.', 1, NOW(), NOW()),
(1, 'Honzu Asahi Competition Grade 本簾朝日', 'ceremonial', 5, 0, 'First Flush (May)', 'Competition grade matcha using traditional Honzu shading with Asahi cultivar. Deep umami, complex layers. Competition Grade - $89/30g retail.', 1, NOW(), NOW()),
(1, 'Suisho 翠初', 'premium', 3, 0, 'First Flush (May)', 'Entry-level matcha latte grade, perfect for daily lattes. Balanced, mild sweetness. Latte Grade 00 - $25/30g retail.', 1, NOW(), NOW()),
(1, 'Ryokuun 緑雲', 'premium', 4, 0, 'First Flush (May)', 'Premium matcha latte grade with enhanced umami. Green cloud smoothness, creamy. Latte Grade 01 - $35/30g retail.', 1, NOW(), NOW()),
(1, 'Seiha 青波', 'premium', 4, 0, 'First Flush (May)', 'Advanced matcha latte grade with ceremonial characteristics. Blue wave freshness, vibrant. Latte Grade 02 - $39/30g retail.', 1, NOW(), NOW()),
(1, 'Samidori Kun さみどり薫', 'ceremonial', 5, 0, 'First Flush (May)', 'Top-tier latte grade using Samidori cultivar. Fragrant Samidori, rich body. Latte Grade 03 - $55/30g retail.', 1, NOW(), NOW()),
(1, 'Najirushi Premium Ceremonial 名印', 'ceremonial', 5, 0, 'First Flush (May)', 'Premium ceremonial grade for cultivar blending experience. Classic ceremonial profile. 10g sample - $37 retail.', 1, NOW(), NOW()),
(1, 'Samidori Competition さみどり', 'ceremonial', 5, 0, 'First Flush (May)', 'Competition grade Samidori cultivar for blending. Sweet, delicate umami. 10g sample - $37 retail.', 1, NOW(), NOW()),
(1, 'Uji Hikari Competition 宇治光', 'ceremonial', 5, 0, 'First Flush (May)', 'Competition grade Uji Hikari cultivar. Bright, luminous character. 10g sample - $37 retail.', 1, NOW(), NOW());
